credit.credit-words: The triumphs of thy love display, In every heart reign thou alone. Till all thy foes confess thy sway, And glory ends what grace began.
Spirit of grace, and health, and power, Fountain of light and love below, Abroad thy healing influence shower, O'er all the nations let it flow.
Blessing and honour, praise and love. Co-equal, co-eternal Three, In earth below, and heaven above, By all thy works be paid on thee!
Thrice Holy! Thine the kingdom is, The power omnipotent is Thine; And when created nature dies, Thy never-ceasing glories shine.
